#: lib/retro_hex_chat/chat/help_topics/commands.ex:277
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Add or remove users from your notify list to track when they connect or disconnect."
msgstr "연결하거나 차단할 때 목록을 지정하거나 삭제할 수 있습니다."

